-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack wxWidgets2.8-2.8.9.2-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./wxWidgets2.8-2.8.9.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libwx_baseu2.8-devel-2.8.9.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libwx_baseu2.8_0-2.8.9.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libwx_gtk2u2.8-devel-2.8.9.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libwx_gtk2u2.8_0-2.8.9.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/python-wx2.8-2.8.9.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/wxWidgets2.8-2.8.9.2-X-src.tar.bz2

A list of files in each package can be found by running:
cygcheck -l PACKAGE [PACKAGE2 ...]

